    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, and I\u2019ve kept it in showroom-perfect condition since day one. It drives like an absolute dream and still has that fresh, new-car feel. No scratches, no dents\u2014just pure perfection! I'm honestly sad to see it go, but I know it\u2019s going to make its next owner so happy. Drop me a message if you want to come take a look!",
      "price": 43900.0,
