    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presented is a collector-grade E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six with high-pressure VANOS and individual throttle bodies for instantaneous throttle response. This example is mechanically pristine, with documented rod bearing replacement and proactive rear subframe reinforcement already completed. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox operates with clinical precision, sending power through a factory limited-slip differential. The chassis retains its original 50/50 weight distribution and torsional rigidity, while the interior shows zero bolster wear or pixel degradation. A turn-key masterpiece for the purist who demands technical perfection and documented provenance.",
      "price": 48500.0,
