    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment, resulting in a factory-fresh appearance that must be seen to be appreciated. The exterior paint retains its deep, mirror-like luster with absolutely no swirl marks, rock chips, or door dings. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom state; the premium leather upholstery shows no creasing or bolster wear, and the original factory scent is still present. Every electronic component, from the high-resolution infotainment system to the multi-zone climate control, operates flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, featuring a complete, documented service history from an authorized technician. Recent preventative maintenance includes a full synthetic oil service, brake fluid flush, and a fresh set of premium tires. This is not just a used car; it is a collector-grade specimen ready for its next discerning owner. Includes all original keys, manuals, and a custom-fit car cover.",
